Split Data into Input Vectors and Output Labels¶

In [4]:
# Input Vectors Train
X_train = np.array(training_data.drop(['label'], axis=1))

# Output Labels Train
Y_train = np.array(training_data['label'])

# Input Vector Test
X_test = np.array(testing_data.drop(['label'], axis=1))

# Output Label Test
Y_test = np.array(testing_data['label'])

Build Neural Network ( 2 Dimentional CNN )¶

Reshape Data¶

In [7]:
# Reshape Training Data
x_train = X_train.reshape(X_train.shape[0], 28, 28, 1)

# Reshape Testing Data
x_test = X_test.reshape(X_test.shape[0], 28, 28, 1)

# Convert y Train to Categorical
y_train = to_categorical(Y_train)

# Convert y Test to Categorical
y_test = to_categorical(Y_test)

Build Model¶

In [8]:
# Build Model

model = Sequential()
model.add(Conv2D(16,kernel_size=(3,3),activation='relu',input_shape=(28, 28, 1)))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))
model.add(Dropout(0.3))

model.add(Conv2D(32,kernel_size=(3,3),activation='relu'))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))
model.add(Dropout(0.3))

model.add(Conv2D(64,kernel_size=(3,3),activation='relu'))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))
model.add(Dropout(0.4))

model.add(Flatten())

model.add(Dense(y_train.shape[1],activation='sigmoid'))

Build Hybrid Model ( CNN-LSTM )¶

Reshape Data¶

In [13]:
# Reshape Training Data
x_train = X_train.reshape(X_train.shape[0], 28, 28)

# Reshape Testing Data
x_test = X_test.reshape(X_test.shape[0], 28, 28)

# Convert y Train to Categorical
y_train = to_categorical(Y_train)

# Convert y Test to Categorical
y_test = to_categorical(Y_test)

Build Model¶

In [14]:
# Build Model

hybrid_model = Sequential()
hybrid_model.add(Conv1D(64, 4, activation='relu', padding='same', input_shape=(28,28)))
hybrid_model.add(LSTM(64, return_sequences=True))
hybrid_model.add(MaxPool1D(2))
hybrid_model.add(Conv1D(128, 8, activation="relu", padding='same'))
hybrid_model.add(LSTM(128, return_sequences=True))
hybrid_model.add(MaxPool1D(2))
hybrid_model.add(Conv1D(256, 8, activation="relu", padding='same'))
hybrid_model.add(LSTM(256))
hybrid_model.add(Dense(25, activation='sigmoid'))

Comparison of Both Models¶

Model 1 ( 2 Dimentional CNN )¶

In [19]:
# Model 1 Scores
X_1 = X_test.reshape(X_test.shape[0], 28, 28, 1)
pred_1 = model.predict(X_1)
pred_1 = np.argmax(pred_1, axis=1)
y = np.argmax(y_test, axis=1)

# Calculate Accuracy
model_1_accuracy = accuracy_score(y,pred_1)

# Calculate Precision
model_1_precision = precision_score(y,pred_1,average='macro')

# Calculate Recall
model_1_recall = recall_score(y,pred_1,average='macro')

# Calculate F1
model_1_f1 = f1_score(y,pred_1,average='macro')

# Print Scores
print("\n\n============================================")
print("    Accuracy Score:   ", model_1_accuracy)
print("    Precision Score:  ", model_1_precision)
print("    Recall Score:     ", model_1_recall)
print("    F1 Score:         ", model_1_f1)
print("============================================\n\n")

# Heat Map
print("\n\n============================================")
print("      Confusion Matrix with Heat MAP:")
print("============================================\n\n")
test_confusion_matrix_heatmap = confusion_matrix(y, pred_1, normalize = 'true')
sns.set(rc={'figure.figsize':(14,7)})
sns.heatmap(test_confusion_matrix_heatmap, annot=True)
plt.show()

Difference¶

In [21]:
# Add the Results in a Pretty Table

pretty_table = PrettyTable()
pretty_table.add_column(" ** Model ** ", ['2D CNN','Hybrid Model'])

pretty_table.add_column(" ** Recall ** ", [round(model_1_recall,2), round(model_2_recall,2)])
pretty_table.add_column(" ** F1 ** ", [round(model_1_f1,2), round(model_2_f1,2)])

# Get a reference to webcam 
video_capture = cv2.VideoCapture(0)

while True:
    ret, frame = video_capture.read()
    frame = cv2.flip(frame, 1)
    rgb_frame = frame[:, :, ::-1]
    window_name = 'Live Detection'
    font = cv2.FONT_HERSHEY_SIMPLEX
    org = (50, 50)
    fontScale = 2
    color = (255, 0, 0)
    thickness = 4
    
    thresh_img = rgb_frame.copy()
    thresh_img = cv2.cvtColor(thresh_img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
    ret, rgb_frame = cv2.threshold(thresh_img, 100, 200, cv2.THRESH_BINARY)
    
    # Get Model Prediction
    resized = cv2.resize(rgb_frame, (28,28), interpolation = cv2.INTER_AREA)
    a = resized[:,:].reshape(1, 28, 28, 1)
    predict = Trained_Model.predict(a)
    
    #confidence = np.max(predict)
    prediction = np.argmax(predict, axis=1)
    
    # Write on Video
    my_str = ''
    if(prediction==0):
        my_str = 'A'
    elif(prediction==1):
        my_str = 'B'
    elif(prediction==2):
        my_str = 'C'
    elif(prediction==3):
        my_str = 'D'
    elif(prediction==4):
        my_str = 'E'        
    elif(prediction==5):
        my_str = 'F'        
    elif(prediction==6):
        my_str = 'G'        
    elif(prediction==7):
        my_str = 'H'       
    elif(prediction==8):
        my_str = 'I'
    elif(prediction==9):
        my_str = 'J'
    elif(prediction==10):
        my_str = 'K'
    elif(prediction==11):
        my_str = 'L' 
    elif(prediction==12):
        my_str = 'M'
    elif(prediction==13):
        my_str = 'N'
    elif(prediction==14):
        my_str = 'O'
    elif(prediction==15):
        my_str = 'P'        
    elif(prediction==16):
        my_str = 'Q'        
    elif(prediction==17):
        my_str = 'R'        
    elif(prediction==18):
        my_str = 'S'       
    elif(prediction==19):
        my_str = 'T'
    elif(prediction==20):
        my_str = 'U'
    elif(prediction==21):
        my_str = 'V'
    elif(prediction==22):
        my_str = 'W'  
    elif(prediction==23):
        my_str = 'X'
    else:
        my_str = 'Y'
    
    cv2.putText(rgb_frame, my_str, org, font, fontScale, color, thickness, cv2.LINE_AA)

        break
